	                            <div id="dsq-comment-text-2758752408" class="dsq-comment-text">
	                                <p>Glad you figured it out! The code you posted will be helpful for other people :).</p><p>For those people, here's the working code for setting a label:</p><p></p><pre><code><br>{# the 2nd argument of *form_label* is just the string label #}<br>{{ form_label(form.title, 'title') }}<br><br>{# the 2nd argument if *form_row* is an array of variables #}<br>{{ form_row(form.title, {'label': 'title'}) }}<br></code></pre><p></p><p>Cheers!</p>
